name: Fattie on a walk
description:
Fattie is a Cat, who, most of the time, is lazy. However, Fattie likes walking from his house to the neighbor's house because he can find some food in the neighbor cat's bowl.  More often Fattie finds food, fewer hungry cats in the world.

50% of the proceeds raised with this kitty will be used to improve the lives of cats around the world.
